= Monsters =

This page documents all monsters in Final Fantasy Mystic Quest for the SNES.

== Monster Statistics ==

=== Data Structure ===

Each monster entry uses 32 bytes:

{| class="wikitable"
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00 || 2 || HP
|-
| $02 || 1 || Attack
|-
| $03 || 1 || Defense
|-
| $04 || 1 || Speed
|-
| $05 || 1 || Magic
|-
| $06 || 2 || Experience
|-
| $08 || 2 || GP
|-
| $0A || 1 || Elemental Weakness
|-
| $0B || 1 || Status Immunity
|-
| $0C-$0F || 4 || Attack Pattern
|-
| $10-$1F || 16 || Sprite/Animation Data
|}

